    <date day="08" month="February" year="2023"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies describes some interoperability issues
   identified between LEDBAT++ and BBR, resulting in unexpected
   behaviour.  Specifically, that under a set of common conditions,
   LEDBAT++ fails to yield in front of both BBRv1 and BBRv2(instead of
   the opposite expected behaviour).</t>
    </abstract>
